## Summary

### TS2322 Regression — Fixed

**Is it a real Phase 5 regression?** Yes. `HomePage.tsx` passed `sections={allSections}` (an array of `{title, items}[]` objects) but `MenuSections` expects `groups: CategoryGroups` (an object with named category arrays). This is both the wrong prop name and wrong shape.

**Does it block the test run?** No. CRA's Jest runner is independent of `tsc --noEmit`. Tests would run even with this TS error. It would block `yarn tsc --noEmit` and `yarn build`.

**Fix applied:** Removed the redundant `allSections` array from `HomePage.tsx` and changed `sections={allSections}` → `groups={groups}` (line 98). `MenuSections` already builds sections internally from `groups`.

